pos_examples: Now, apply the action "drop" to rover screen and store dress_red.
Once you are done, please apply the action "calibrate" to rover fire, camera kumquat, objective yew and waypoint rain.

First, apply the action "communicate_soil_data" to rover fire, lander roof_11, waypoint star_213, waypoint rain and waypoint star_213_70 and then apply the action "navigate" to rover screen, waypoint star_213 and waypoint star_213_38.

(communicate_soil_data fire roof_11 star_213 rain star_213_70)
(navigate screen star_213 star_213_38)
The next step is to apply the action "communicate_image_data" to rover fire, lander frame_9, objective object_260, mode bastion, waypoint star_213_38 and waypoint star_213.
(communicate_image_data fire frame_9 object_260 bastion star_213_38 star_213)
